{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"94795-who-s-that-baby","title":"Qui est ce bébé ?","description":"Un nouveau bébé est venu jouer à la maison. Qui est ce bébé ?","language":"French","langCode":"fr","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Sak Untala"],"illustrators":["Natalie Hinrichsen","Tamsin Hinrichsen"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/94795-who-s-that-baby"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/130509/size3/484341a5bc300b5b5a3a9b2493a7b74d.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/130509/size6/484341a5bc300b5b5a3a9b2493a7b74d.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129060/size6/f0db1a5a320c2e3276a84c46d078a7a1.jpg","text":"Coucou !","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129061/size6/6ac4636dfbea75dc38a4cd922130f23e.jpg","text":"Qui est ce bébé ?","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129062/size6/482837b49996963616c58d0048c1e437.jpg","text":"Ce bébé sait marcher.\nComme moi.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129063/size6/a31849cba95c393a1addedfe9410d706.jpg","text":"Mes orteils se tortillent. Les orteils de ce bébé se tortillent aussi !","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129064/size6/a9870b41dac5a7e26ae04ccea02bfd33.jpg","text":"Oh, le bébé a disparu !","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129065/size6/b6e2ce21d99fba553e6d46c69952e047.jpg","text":"Qui est ce bébé ?","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129066/size6/abb37d54596738f07ee793982ade17d0.jpg","text":"J'agite mes mains.\nCe bébé agite ses mains aussi.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129067/size6/bb07b520cf8d19332553ace5f7f9a981.jpg","text":"Tu veux jouer avec moi ?","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129068/size6/2d2a709666462096b5020be7329fbad8.jpg","text":"Oh, non, ce bébé a encore disparu !","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129069/size6/a4cb156463e3d745a33727b259d29ffc.jpg","text":"Qui est ce bébé ?","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129070/size6/791dceaafc77ba37a574195bc5175d2e.jpg","text":"J'ai un petit nez adorable. Ce bébé a un petit nez adorable aussi.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129071/size6/81b74d7a78665665c61b458aefe6340c.jpg","text":"Je fais une grimace.\nCe bébé fait une grimace aussi.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129072/size6/606f66d7615a8224e89b317b7a1e893b.jpg","text":"Oh, mais ce bébé, c'est...\nMOI !","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129073/size6/33d0b34bbefa328ac17ed4ac1628a6be.jpg","text":"Au revoir !","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/129074/size6/89d72b32aad57b6114ad4ada23131834.jpg","text":"16/16","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":15,"words":99}}